item.title: CVE-2016-8334|2024-08-06T02:20:30.475Z -- foxit%20software -- foxit%20reader
item.description: A large out-of-bounds read on the heap vulnerability in Foxit PDF Reader can potentially be abused for information disclosure. Combined with another vulnerability, it can be used to leak heap memory layout and in bypassing ASLR.
